      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 750ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[975ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>thyme leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p>",
