    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> when the rice is nearly cooked – this is your<strong> cherry tomato</strong> <strong>risotto</strong></p><p>Once cooked, remove the <strong>risotto</strong> from the heat then add your<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and stir through</p><p>Taste for seasoning adding more<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p>",
