    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Add your <strong>meat-free bacon </strong>to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until golden and crispy</p><p>Remove the <strong>cooked meat-free bacon</strong> from the pan and chop roughly</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and add to a bowl with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong></p>",
