      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cherry tomato</strong> <strong>risotto</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>meat-free bacon</strong> over the risotto</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
